WEBVTT

00:02.662 --> 00:05.580
New friends are all around the world.

00:06.744 --> 00:09.916
Some are like you, and some are different.

00:10.947 --> 00:13.899
I am Chang-Yong, and I am ten.

00:14.965 --> 00:17.535
My family lives in South Korea.

00:18.677 --> 00:21.846
I like going to school and playing ball.

00:22.650 --> 00:25.207
My best jacket is made of silk.

00:25.978 --> 00:29.279
My favorite food is barbecued beef.

00:30.535 --> 00:32.361
Jessica is my name.

00:33.339 --> 00:35.057
I live in Australia.

00:35.444 --> 00:36.643
I am six.

00:37.663 --> 00:40.386
I live with my mother and grandmother.

00:41.255 --> 00:43.166
My mother is a cook.

00:43.851 --> 00:47.065
I love to watch kangaroos hop around.

00:48.375 --> 00:51.254
I am Natasha, and I am seven.

00:52.455 --> 00:55.564
My home is an apartment in Moscow, Russia.

00:56.674 --> 00:57.998
I like dancing.

00:58.833 --> 01:01.587
I wear a fur hat and coat in winter.

01:02.384 --> 01:03.907
I play in the snow.

01:04.667 --> 01:06.618
I love to eat pancakes.

01:07.857 --> 01:10.057
I live in Tanzania.

01:11.263 --> 01:13.552
Manka is my name.

01:14.771 --> 01:17.562
We live in a hut with a grass roof.

01:18.554 --> 01:21.471
My father takes care of our cows.

01:22.251 --> 01:24.367
I get water from a well.

01:25.085 --> 01:27.427
I make toys out of clay.

01:28.655 --> 01:30.435
I am Kipanik.

01:31.141 --> 01:33.945
I live in Canada, where it is cold.

01:34.716 --> 01:37.245
My dogs pull me on my sled.

01:37.945 --> 01:40.117
I play hockey with my friends.

01:40.823 --> 01:43.576
Our dads hunt animals for food.

01:44.261 --> 01:46.216
I like meat with ketchup.

01:47.279 --> 01:49.653
How are you like these children.

01:50.161 --> 01:51.651
How are you different.

